   NCONS=1 NO_STORM (one consumer, one producer, zero signals) HANGS after
   ~4.1M iterations with work=621 (>0) and the consumer asleep in
   pthread_cond_wait, never woken. Pure lost cond_signal, no EINTR/abort/storm.

