   (guest libpthread <-> server duct-tape _psynch_cvwait/psynch_cvsignal ksyn
   machinery), NOT the sigexc/signal-abort path. bd7cdb9 (TH_WAIT routing) and
   5766b1d (mutex double-insert) target the wrong layer. 65038e3 (uninit
   mutex_link) remains a correct standalone fix.

